name: JUNKIE
description: Junk which means trash that is thrown away and not used anymore which has a negative impression, while junkie can be used as an addict for something that has a negative connotation, in this work tells the phenomenon of teenagers who are already addicted to goods, illegal drugs, etc., they destroy themselves themselves without knowing the consequences, all they enjoy is having fun!, they think it's a way out for them to solve problems. Everyone saw what they were doing.
